"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "1355: providence",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1355",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The continuing and often unseen activity of God in sustaining his universe, providing for the needs of every creature, and preparing for the completion of his eternal purposes.</p>\n<h2>God's general providence</h2>\n<h3>God sustains the created order</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a></strong> <em>A promise given by God to all peoples.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:6\">NEH 9:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:26\">ISA 40:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:17\">COL 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>All life is dependent on God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:13\">1TI 6:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:27\">1SA 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:21\">JOB 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:3\">PSA 127:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:2\">ECC 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:9\">ECC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:16\">EZK 24:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:26\">DAN 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:4\">MAT 4:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>God controls the elements</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8\">PSA 147:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job37:1-Job37:13\">JOB 37:1–37:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps29:3-Ps29:9\">PSA 29:3–29:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:6-Ps135:7\">PSA 135:6–135:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">MAT 5:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25-Acts17:28\">ACT 17:25–17:28</a></p>\n<h3>God provides for the created world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:15-Ps145:16\">PSA 145:15–145:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:39-Job38:41\">JOB 38:39–38:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:27-Ps104:28\">PSA 104:27–104:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:25\">PSA 136:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:9\">PSA 147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:6-Luke12:7\">LUK 12:6–12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>God's providence through miraculous means</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:9-Job5:10\">JOB 5:9–5:10</a></strong> <em>God's regular activity in providing for human beings is regarded as being miraculous in just the same way as special demonstrations of his power.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:11-Exod16:14\">EXO 16:11–16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:28-Num16:35\">NUM 16:28–16:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:18-Judg15:19\">JDG 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:5-1Kgs17:6\">1KI 17:5–17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:42-2Kgs4:44\">2KI 4:42–4:44</a></p>\n<h2>God's providence in human history</h2>\n<h3>God's control of human intentions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:12\">HAB 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:19-1Kgs22:20\">1KI 22:19–22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:27-2Kgs19:28\">2KI 19:27–19:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:28-Isa37:29\">ISA 37:28–37:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:15\">ISA 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab1:6\">HAB 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's providential actions on behalf of individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12\">JOB 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6\">JOB 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:12-Ps107:14\">PSA 107:12–107:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:24-Ps107:29\">PSA 107:24–107:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:33-Ps107:38\">PSA 107:33–107:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:17\">ISA 38:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's saving purposes fulfilled through providence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:20\">GEN 50:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:13\">GEN 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:5-Gen45:8\">GEN 45:5–45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">2CH 36:22–36:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:3\">EZR 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:14\">EZR 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:28-Isa45:1\">ISA 44:28–45:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:27-Acts4:28\">ACT 4:27–4:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a></p>\n<h2>God's providence prepares for the completion of his ultimate purpose</h2>\n<h3>God is forming a people for himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:3\">REV 21:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod6:7\">EXO 6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:14-Eph2:16\">EPH 2:14–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3-1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:3–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9\">REV 7:9</a></p>\n<h3>God will bring all things under Jesus Christ's authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:9-Eph1:10\">EPH 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:22-Isa45:23\">ISA 45:22–45:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:23\">ISA 66:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:24-1Cor15:26\">1CO 15:24–15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:10-Phil2:11\">PHP 2:10–2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:20\">COL 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></p>\n<h3>God will complete his purpose for creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:20-Rom8:21\">ROM 8:20–8:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a></p>\n<h3>God directs all things for his glory</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:36\">ROM 11:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps46:10\">PSA 46:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:23\">ROM 9:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:36\">ROM 11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:4-Eph1:6\">EPH 1:4–1:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11-Eph1:12\">EPH 1:11–1:12</a></p>",
